 * Emits the wasi_snapshot_preview1 adapter shim (core module 1) that bridges
 * the preview1 ABI expected by nexus core wasm to the preview2 canon-lowered
 * functions.  Six variants: has_fs × (no_net | has_net_no_srv | has_net_has_srv).
